data.description: Welcome home to this meticulously maintained beauty nestled in the sought-after Sedgefield Community of Dallas! Situated on a serene cul-de-sac lot with a THREE car garage! This home boasts a spacious kitchen perfect for all of your culinary needs. Counter space will never be an issue again! Flowing open floor plan. Escape to the luxurious primary suite on the main level, featuring an extremely large bedroom and a spa-like newly renovated ensuite bathroom for ultimate relaxation. A convenient additional guest suite on the main level provides extra comfort. Three additional bedrooms upstairs are generous in size. Formal dining room, a large open fire-side great room with 20+ft soaring ceilings. Plenty of storage throughout the home. Step outside to your own private oasis, complete with a screened-in porch, ideal for enjoying the outdoors year-round. With its fantastic location near dining, schools, and shopping, this home offers the perfect blend of comfort and convenience. Don't miss your chance to make this dreamy retreat yours!
